📂 Featured Project: The Giddy's AI Agent
A Full-Stack Customer Support & Logistics Orchestrator

I engineered a custom AI chatbot for Giddy's, a regional online cake shop (serving Kisumu & Homabay). This project demonstrates the integration of complex logic with real-world business tools.

The Architecture:
Deployment: Docker-based n8n instance hosted via Render for reliable webhook management.

Brain: OpenAI GPT-4o with Window Buffer Memory nodes for persistent context tracking (cake flavors, delivery preferences).

Security: Full OAuth2 implementation via Google Cloud for secure API handshakes.

Interdependent Tools (The Action Layer):

Google Calendar Tool: Automatically schedules delivery events.

Google Sheets Tool: Real-time order logging and customer database management.

Custom JavaScript/JSON: Logic-gated delivery validation (restricting orders to specific counties).

Marketing Extension: A secondary n8n workflow using HTTP Requests to automatically generate social media content based on inventory/order trends.

